ing company with interests in the beverage and malting industries as the representative of beverage associates bac corp from  to  mr engels served in various capacities at quinsa including director of mergers and acquisitions group controller and manager of corporate finance prior to joining quinsa mr engels served as a vice president at citibank na in london responsible for european sales of latin american investment products and in brazil in the area of mergers and acquisitions since  mr engels has served as deputy chairman of the board of mutual investment limited mr engels has also served as a member of the board of bisa a fund with diversified investments in different industries mr engels holds a bs from babson college an ma from the university of pennsylvania and an mba from the wharton school of the university of pennsylvania mr engels brings to the board significant financial experience an understanding of mergers and acquisitions and a good understanding of industrial and consumer products companies he brings an international business perspective to the board having had extensive working experience in europe the united states and latin america he also qualifies as an audit committee financial expert source bunge limited on    sign up for equilar atlas and view william engelss full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like william engels more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in william engelss network and community follow changes in william engelss employment and moneyinmotion connect with william engels through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example william engels william engelss connections  sign up now to view william engelss  connections » brian thomsen managing director bunge global agribusiness and chief executive officer bunge product lines bunge limited soren schroder chief executive officer