al has been so often translated in germany it has had four editions of about  copies in all  cited in carver terrell  engels a very short introduction oxford university press p   and thomas paul  critical reception marx then and now in carver terrell the cambridge companion to marx cambridge university press   marxistsanueduauarchivemarxworksdon sourcesedit carlton grace  friedrich engels the shadow prophet london pall mall press carver terrell  friedrich engels his life and thought london macmillan green john  engels a revolutionary life london artery publications isbn  henderson w o  the life of friedrich engels london  cass  isbn  hunt tristram  the frockcoated communist the revolutionary life of friedrich engels london allen lane isbn  mayer gustav  friedrich engels a biography  trans  external linksedit wikimedia commons has media related to friedrich engels wikiquote has quotations related to friedrich engels wikisource has original works written by or about friedrich engels marxengels biographical archive the legend of marx or engels the founder by maximilien rubel reason in revolt marxism and modern science engels the che guevara of his day the brave new world tristram hunt on marx and engels revolutionary vision german biography from dhmde frederick engels a biography engels was right early human kinship was matriliineal works by engelsedit the marx  engels internet archive at marxistsorg works by friedrich engels at project gutenberg works by or about friedrich engels at internet archive works by friedrich engels at librivox public domain audiobooks libcomorglibrary friedrich engels archive works by friedrich engels in german at zenoorg pathfinder press friedrich engels on rifled cannon articles from the new york tribune april may and june  reprinted in military affairs  no  winter  ed morton borden – marx and engels in their native german language v t e works by karl marx and friedrich engels marx capital capital volume i  capital volume ii  posthumous ca