ftwing politics communist parties with parliamentary representation progressivism new class new left red scare workers of the world unite naxalite insurgency anthem the internationale communism portal authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  selibr  sudoc  bnf cb data ulan  hds  musicbrainz fcedebecec nla  ndl  nkc jn iccu iticcucfiv bne xx retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlefriedrichengelsoldid categories  births deathsthcentury atheistsdeaths from throat cancerpeople from the province of jülichclevesbergpeople from wuppertalthcentury economiststhcentury philosophersthcentury german writersthcentury prussian peopleatheist philosophersgerman atheistsgerman political philosophersgerman communistsgerman economistsgerman emigrants to englandgerman feministsgerman revolutionarieskarl marxmale feministsmarxist feministsmarxist theoristsmarxist writerscommunist writersantinationalistsmaterialistsmembers of the international workingmens associationorthodox marxistspeople of the revolutions of prussian army personneltheories of historyurban theoristsbritish industrialistsgerman philosopherspeople from the rhine provincesocialist economistsgerman atheism activistsantitheistsatheist writersatheist socialistshidden categories wikipedia pending changes protected pages level use dmy dates from october use british english from december interlanguage link template link numberbiography with signaturearticles with hcardsall articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statements from june articles with unsourced statements from january articles with unsourced statements from september articles with project gutenberg linksarticles with internet archive linksarticles with librivox linksac with  elementswikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles with isni identifierswikipedia articles with gnd identifierswikipedia articles with selibr identifierswikipedia articles with bnf identifi