uide to famous graves london fourth estate limited p  isbn    manchester photographers by gillian read ed royal photographic societys historical group  george lester  king street manchester – see the photo in jenny marx album too  engels friedrich friedrich engelss confession marxists internet archive archived from the original on  april  retrieved    marxs general the revolutionary life of friedrich engels by tristram hunt  p   paul lafargue jacques bonhomme  august  friedrich engels marxists internet archive from the social democrat journal marxists internet archive retrieved  april    vladimir ilyich lenin friedrich engels marxistsorg retrieved    robert service comrades a world history of communism london macmillan  p   thomas paul  critical reception marx then and now in carver terrell the cambridge companion to marx cambridge university press pp –   friedrich engels beard inspires climbing sculpture in salford bbc  retrieved    a b the holy family by marx and engels marxistsorg retrieved    griffin emma the industrial revolution interpretations from  to the present retrieved  march    engels friedrich   introduction socialism utopian and scientific marxengels selected works  progress publishers from this french text a polish and a spanish edition were prepared in  our german friends brought out the pamphlet in the original language italian russian danish dutch and roumanian translations based upon the german text have since been published thus the present english edition this little book circulates in  languages i am not aware that any other socialist work not even our communist manifesto of  or marxs capital has been so often translated in germany it has had four editions of about  copies in all  cited in carver terrell  engels a very short introduction oxford university press p   and thomas paul  critical reception marx then and now in carver terrell the cambridge companion to marx cambridge university press   marxistsanueduauarchivemarxworksdon sourcesedit 